            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab><persName key="#Other_clerics" ref="#people/703">Ermipert</persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_clerics">clerico</rs>, quia ante hos annos sanctae
                        recordande memoriae <persName key="#Imperial/royal_diploma #Emperor/king"
                            ref="#people/48">Aistulf</persName>
                        <rs key="#Emperor/king">rex</rs> per suum <rs key="#Imperial/royal_diploma"
                            >cessionis preceptum</rs> donavet et confirmavet <rs key="#Churches"
                            >ecclesia</rs> et <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_individuals #Churches #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/283">Sancti Petri</orgName> fundato a quondam
                            <persName key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Inflow #Churches #Monasteries"
                            ref="#people/704"><name ref="Sumualdus">Sumuald</name></persName>, hic
                        prope <rs key="#Walls">muro</rs> huius<placeName key="#Cities #Walls"
                            ref="#places/4">
                            <rs key="#Cities">civitatis</rs></placeName>, cum omnia ividem
                        pertenente in integrum, <persName
                            key="#Imperial/royal_diploma #Offersio/donatio #Specialized_workers"
                            ref="#people/390">Auripert</persName>
                        <rs key="#Specialized_workers">pictori</rs> germani meo, ut in eius esset
                        potestate regendi, gubernandi, usufructuandi et ordinandi, qualiter ei
                        placitum fuerit; et postea per <rs key="#Offersio/donatio">cartulam
                            firmationis</rs> me in ipsa <rs key="#Churches">eclesia</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Offersio/donatio #Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_individuals #Churches #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/283">Sancti Petri</orgName> in omnibus ordinare
                        et confirmare visus est, secundum qualiter eum, ut dixi bone memorie Aistulf
                        rex in ipso monasterio confirmaverat, nisi tantum die vite sue usufructu de
                        ipso monasterio in suo reservavit dominio. Et ego petivi excellentia domno
                        meo <persName key="#Imperial/royal_diploma #Emperor/king" ref="#people/249"
                            >Desiderio</persName>
                        <rs key="#Emperor/king">regi</rs>, ut per suum <rs
                            key="#Imperial/royal_diploma">preceptum</rs> predictam <rs
                            key="#Offersio/donatio">donationis et firmationis mei paginam</rs>
                        confirmaret; ita et factum est. Nunc vero presenti per hanc paginam bona mea
                        voluntate qualiter iam dicto germano meo in me ipsa <rs key="#Churches"
                            >eclesia</rs> et <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Imperial/royal_diploma #Offersio/donatio #Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_individuals #Churches #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/283">Sancti Petri</orgName> confirmavet,
                        similiter et ego confirmare prevideo te domno meo viro beatissimo <persName
                            key="#Bishops" ref="#people/343">Peredeo</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopo</rs> in ipsa eclesia et monasterio ut cunctis
                        diebus in tua et de successoribus tuis sit potestate ividem ordinatione et
                        inperatione faciendo in omnibus, qualiter Deo et vobis recte et melius
                        apparuerit; nisi tantum volo adque instituo ut, dum ego advivere meruero, in
                        mea sit potestate regendi, inperandi et usufructuandi tantum, non in alio
                        homine aut in eclesia iterum confirmando. <foreign>Poi passi definitivamente
                            al vescovo.</foreign> Actum <placeName ref="#places/4">Luca</placeName>.
                            <foreign>Sottoscrizioni</foreign>: (ss) Ermipert clericus; (ss)
                            <persName key="#Witness #Priests"><name ref="Ragibrandus"
                                >Rachiprand</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbiter</rs>; (ss) <persName key="#Witness #Subdeacons"
                                ><name ref="Perprandus">Periprandus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Subdeacons">subdiaconus</rs>; (ss) <persName
                            key="#Witness #Other_clerics"><name ref="Petronax"
                            >Petronaci</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_clerics">clericus</rs>; (ss) <persName
                            key="#Witness #Other_clerics"><name ref="Alabrandus"
                            >Alaprandu</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_clerics">clericus</rs>; (ss) <persName
                            key="#Witness #Other_clerics"><name ref="Sprinca"
                            >Isprinca</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_clerics">clericus</rs>. <foreign>Scrive</foreign>: <persName
                            key="#Writer #Deacons"><name ref="Osprandus">Osprandus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Deacons">diaconus</rs>. [<foreign>Copia</foreign>: <persName
                            key="#Copyist #Priests"><name ref="Gumbertus"
                            >Gumpertus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbiter</rs>].</ab>
                        </div>
                    </div>
